OL,3,CJohn Smyth QC abuse survivor calls for
OL,4,C'clean sweep' of Church of England
OL,6,FAn abuse survivor has echoed calls for
OL,7,Fthe Archbishop of Canterbury to resign
OL,8,Fas he demanded a "clean sweep" of
OL,9,Fsenior clergy members.
OL,11,FMark Stibbe, who was abused by John
OL,12,FSmyth QC in the 1980s, told BBC
OL,13,FNewsnight on Monday that Justin
OL,14,FWelby's position was "untenable" after
OL,15,Fan independent review published last
OL,16,Fweek concluded that Smyth might have
OL,17,Fbeen brought to justice had the
OL,18,Farchbishop formally reported the abuse
OL,19,Fto police a decade ago.
