OL,6,FThe recent Makin review described the
OL,7,Fnow deceased John Smyth as "sadistic"
OL,8,Fand the most prolific abuser
OL,9,Fassociated with the Church of England.
OL,11,FMr Stibbe told TV presenter Victoria
OL,12,FDerbyshire: "I honestly don't believe
OL,13,Fthat Justin Welby can continue ` I
OL,14,Fdon't believe that his position is
OL,15,Ftenable.
OL,17,F"I would also apply that to the
OL,18,Fbishops that knew and did nothing, and
OL,19,Fthe senior clergy of the Church of
OL,20,FEngland that knew and did nothing.
