OL,6,F"Their positions are also untenable."
OL,8,FCommenting on a statement from the
OL,9,Fbishop of Newcastle Helen-Ann Hartley,
OL,10,Fwho said earlier on Monday the Church
OL,11,Fof England risked losing its "moral
OL,12,Fvoice" if the situation persisted, Mr
OL,13,FStibbe called for a "clean sweep" of
OL,14,Fthe senior clergy following the
OL,15,Fpublication of the report.
OL,17,FHe said: "There needs to be a clean
OL,18,Fsweep of the hierarchy, and new people
OL,19,Fneed to be put in position ` people
OL,20,Flike the bishop of Newcastle who has
OL,21,Fspoken out so courageously today.
