OL,6,FOver five decades between the 1970s
OL,7,Funtil his death, John Smyth QC is said
OL,8,Fto have subjected as many as 130 boys
OL,9,Fand young men in the UK and Africa to
OL,10,Ftraumatic physical, sexual,
OL,11,Fpsychological and spiritual attacks,
OL,12,Fpermanently marking their lives.
OL,14,FSmyth died aged 75 in Cape Town in
OL,15,F2018 while under investigation by
OL,16,FHampshire Police, and was "never
OL,17,Fbrought to justice for the abuse", the
OL,18,FMakin Review published last week said.
