OL,11,F"vulnerable people like myself who
OL,12,Fwere missing their home, missing their
OL,13,Fparents".
OL,15,FMr Stibbe said Smyth had a shed at his
OL,16,Fhome outside Winchester which had been
OL,17,F"sound-proofed and built for his
OL,18,Fabuses".
