OL,6,FFather Alex Frost, the vicar of St
OL,7,FMatthew's Church Burnley and a General
OL,8,FSynod member for Blackburn Diocese,
OL,9,Ftold Times Radio on Monday night that
OL,10,Fthe Church of England's handling of
OL,11,FJohn Smyth's abuse has caused
OL,12,F"devastating" damage to the
OL,13,Finstitution.
OL,15,FHe said: "I think that the
OL,16,FArchbishop's position, unfortunately,
OL,17,Fhas become untenable. And the damage
OL,18,Fthat it is leaving to the wider Church
OL,19,Fof England is quite devastating.
